Package com.enttribe.hrms.service

Interface EmployeeService

All Superinterfaces:
GenericService<com.enttribe.hrms.model.Employee>
All Known Implementing Classes:
EmployeeServiceImpl
public interface EmployeeService extends GenericService<com.enttribe.hrms.model.Employee>
EmployeeService interface is a service layer interface which handles all the business logic related to Employee model. It extends GenericService interface which provides basic CRUD operations.
